=== URL Parse ===
scheme: https
host: api.example.com
port: 8080
path: /users
query: name=alice&age=30
fragment: section
params: {name: alice, age: 30}
=== URL Encode/Decode ===
encoded: hello%20world%20%26%20special%3Dchars
decoded: hello world & special=chars
=== Env (.env file) ===
{DB_HOST: localhost, DB_PORT: 5432, DB_NAME: myapp, SECRET_KEY: abc123, DEBUG: true}
HOME: /Users/gabriel_aderaldo
=== Done! ===
